          <h1 class="postTitle">Hidden vegetables sauce pasta</h1>
          <h6 class="postDate">1 June 2023</h6>
          <img src="images/pasta.jpg" alt="pasta" id="imgSize" />
          <h4 class="subTitle">INGREDIENTS:</h4>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>
              chopped vegetables: Onion, garlic, carrot, potato, broccoil,
              tomato
            </li>
            <li>olive oil</li>
            <li>tomato paste</li>
            <li>dried oregano</li>
            <li>Any kind of pasta you perfer</li>
            <li>any type of cheese your child like</li>
          </ul>
          <h4 class="subTitle">STPES:</h4>
          <ol class="list">
            <li>add olive oil, Onion and garlic to pan and cook unitl</li>
            <li>after that add chopped tomato</li>
            <li>boil poasta, carrot, potato and broccoil</li>
            <li>add the boilled vegetables to pan and mix</li>
            <li>add tomato paste and dried oregano and mix</li>
            <li>
              put the mix in blender. after it become smooth put it back to the
              pan
            </li>
            <li>
              Finally add the boilled pasta and cheese. let it set and cheese
              melt, then servie it.
            </li>
          </ol>
